Vaporeon (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0133: Eevee
Pokémon
#0135: Jolteon →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Vaporeon (TCG Pocket).

Vaporeon has been featured on 29 different cards since it debuted in the Jungle expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Vaporeon cards are normally Water-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Vaporeon

Vaporeon
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
